2.1 爬虫

import requests
from lxml import etree
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd

def tail_num2aircraft_type(tailnum):
    url = 'https://zh.flightaware.com/live/flight/' + tailnum
    data = requests.get(url).text
    s = etree.HTML(data)
    aircrafttype = s.xpath('/html/head/title/text()')[0]
    ## It is a sentence like "N832UA … History (A319 owned by …",
    ## therefore, we split the string to get the aircraft type.
    ## Sometimes the sentence may be not in that form, just try again.
    if '(' in aircrafttype:
        aircrafttype = aircrafttype.split('(')[1].split()[0]
    return aircrafttype

## There will be an error if the file name contains Chinese,
## so I have to rename the original file as American2018.csv,
## however, without changing the content of the original file.
data = pd.DataFrame(pd.read_csv("American2018.csv"))
tail_nums = data['TAIL_NUM'].unique()  # take the TAIL_NUM column
aircraft_types = []                    # initialize the output list

## For each tail_num, use the defined function to get its aircraft_type.
for index, tail_num in enumerate(tail_nums):
    aircraft_type = tail_num2aircraft_type(tail_num)
    aircraft_types.append(aircraft_type)  # add to output list
    print(index + 1, aircraft_type)       # print for examine

## Create output DataFrame and then output as a csv file.
output = {"TAIL_NUM": tail_nums, "AIRCRAFT_TYPE": aircraft_types}
output = pd.DataFrame(output)
output.to_csv('L_AIRCRAFT_TYPE.csv', encoding = "utf-8", index = False)

data1 <- data_succ
# 时间作四舍五入到半点

data1$CRS_DT <- as.ITime(paste(data1$CRS_DEP_TIME %/% 100, data1$CRS_DEP_TIME %% 100 %/% 30 * 30, sep = ':'))

#以到达为基准时间的延误信息
AT_delay <- ddply(data1, .(CRS_AT), summarize, delay_arrival_cnt = sum(delay), total_arrival_cnt = length(CRS_AT), delay_arrival_rate = delay_arrival_cnt / total_arrival_cnt)
#以出发为基准时间的延误信息
DT_delay <- ddply(data1, .(CRS_DT), summarize, delay_departure_cnt = sum(DEP_DELAY > 14), total_departure_cnt = length(CRS_DT), delay_departure_rate = delay_departure_cnt / total_departure_cnt)

# k折交叉验证
# dat是数据集，k0决定了几折交叉验证
pred.lg1<-function(dat, k0)
{
  pred <- numeric(nrow(dat))
  ind <- sample(1 : k0, nrow(dat), replace = TRUE) #分组
  for (i in 1 : k0)
  {
    ii <- which(ind == i)
    glm.fit <- glm(delay~.,data = dat[-ii, ],family = binomial(link = logit)) # 对于每个组，用剩下的组做逻辑线性回归
    pred[ii] <- predict(glm.fit, dat[ii, ], type = "response") #根据每个回归的结果做预测
  }
  as.data.frame(pred)
}
pred1 <- pred.lg1(data_regression, 10)
# 提取捕获率和覆盖率信息
pred1 <- cbind(data_regression$delay,pred1)
names(pred1) = c("Delay or not",'prob')
pred1 <- pred1[order(-pred1$prob),]
pred1[which(pred1$`Delay or not` == T),][1] = 1
pred1[which(pred1$`Delay or not` == F),][1] = 0
n <- nrow(pred1)
coverage <- seq(1,n)
capture <- rep(0,n+1)
for (i in 2:(n+1)) {
  capture[i] <- capture[i-1] + pred1[i-1,1]
}
capture <- capture[-1]
coverage <- coverage/n
capture <- capture/(nrow(pred1[which(pred1[1]==1),]))
# 合并覆盖率和捕获率信息
pred_plot1 <- cbind(as.data.frame(coverage),as.data.frame(capture))
# 捕获率曲线作图
p <- ggplot(data = pred_plot1) + geom_line(aes(coverage,capture),colour = "yellowgreen",size = 1) +

# k折交叉验证
# dat是数据集，k0决定了几折交叉验证
pred.lg2<-function(dat, k0)
{
  pred <- numeric(nrow(dat))
  ind <- sample(1 : k0, nrow(dat), replace = TRUE) #分组
  for (i in 1 : k0)
  {
    ii <- which(ind == i)
    glm.fit <- glm(delay ~ Summer + Winter + `AH5-16` + `DH5-12` + `Medium Carrier` + `Small Carrier` + LOW_SAT + MEDIAN_TUE_WED_SUN +  C + E + M + `dist 1200 ~ infinity` + `dist 250 ~ 550` + `Median-size Origin Airport` + `Small Origin Airport` + `Median-size Dest Airport` + `Small Dest Airport` ,data = dat[-ii, ], family = binomial(link = logit)) # 对于每个组，用剩下的组做逻辑线性回归
    pred[ii] <- predict(glm.fit, dat[ii, ], type = "response") #根据每个回归的结果做预测
  }
  as.data.frame(pred)
}
# 十折交叉验证
pred2 <- pred.lg2(data_regression, 10)
# 提取捕获率和覆盖率信息
pred2 <- cbind(data_regression$delay,pred2)
names(pred2) = c("Delay or not",'prob')
pred2 <- pred2[order(-pred2$prob),]
pred2[which(pred2$`Delay or not` == T),][1] = 1
pred2[which(pred2$`Delay or not` == F),][1] = 0
n <- nrow(pred2)
coverage <- seq(1,n)
capture <- rep(0,n+1)
for (i in 2:(n+1)) {
  capture[i] <- capture[i-1] + pred2[i-1,1]
}
capture <- capture[-1]
coverage <- coverage/n
capture <- capture/(nrow(pred2[which(pred2[1]==1),]))
# 合并覆盖率和捕获率信息
pred_plot2 <- cbind(as.data.frame(coverage),as.data.frame(capture))
# 捕获率曲线作图
p <- ggplot(data = pred_plot2) + geom_line(aes(coverage,capture),colour = "yellowgreen",size = 1) +
  geom_ribbon(aes(coverage,ymin = 0,ymax = capture),fill = alpha("yellowgreen",0.5)) +
  labs(title ="Capture rate v.s. Coverage") +
  xlab("Coverage") +

3.2 树模型

delay.data =fread("./tree_based_feature.csv")     #读取数据集
delay.data= as.data.frame(delay.data)

delay.data2=delay.data %>% mutate_if(is.character, as.factor) #将数据集中的character数据列转化为因子
delay.data2$delay <-factor(delay.data2$delay)   #  将delay这一列 转化为因子
delay.data <- delay.data2[,2:11]     # 将DEP_DEALY这数据列排除

3.2.1 运用决策树算法

set.seed(123)
#欠采样来获得高捕获率
delay_true <- delay.data[which(delay.data$delay == T),]
delay_false <- delay.data[which(delay.data$delay == F),]
i <- sample(1:nrow(delay_true),10000,F)
j <- sample(1:nrow(delay_false),7000,F)
train_data <- rbind(delay_true[i,],delay_false[j,])
test_data <-  rbind(delay_true[-i,],delay_false[-j,])
tree.model <- rpart(delay~.,method='class',data=train_data) 
tree.predict<-predict(tree.model,newdata= test_data,type='class') 
#对测试集进行预测
tree.table <-table(tree.predict,test_data$delay)
tree.accuracy <- (sum(diag(tree.table)))/sum(tree.table) #对测试集进行预测
tree.table

3.2.3 提升树

set.seed(123)
# boosting模型
train <- adaboost(delay ~.,data=train_data,nIter=100)  
boost.imp = train$trees$`0`$variable.importance  
set.seed(123)
# boosting预测
a<- predict(train,newdata=test_data)
boost.table<- table(a$class,test_data$delay)
boost.accuracy<-(sum(diag(boost.table)))/sum(boost.table)
